719516f-a.title: Manhattan: Houston Street (East) - Mangin Street
719516f-a.text:
East Houston Street (left), at the S.E. corner of Mangin Street,
showing a clearance, and the rear of a warehouse facing on Tompkins
Street. Also shown (background) are the suspension towers of the Williams-
burg Bridge.
June 4, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
